snippet.title: Learn How To Pronounce Amber Heard | Hollywood Actress
snippet.description:
Learn the proper way to say and pronounce the name Amber Heard, a Hollywood Actress.

Amber Laura Heard is an American actress and model. Heard made her film debut in acclaimed sports drama Friday Night Lights, starring Billy Bob Thornton.

Born: April 22, 1986 (age 29), Austin, Texas, United States

Height: 1.73 m

Spouse: Johnny Depp (m. 2015)

Upcoming movie: Magic Mike XXL

Awards: Young Hollywood Award for Breakthrough Performance
